      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link href="/2025/02/08/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/2025/02/08/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>欢迎光临<a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>！这是你的第一篇文章。查看[documentation]（<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/%EF%BC%89%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%97%B6%E9%81%87%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%A8[%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4]%EF%BC%88https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E4%BD%A0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%A8[GitHub]%EF%BC%88https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8A%E9%97%AE%E6%88%91%E3%80%82">https://hexo.io/docs/）获取更多信息。如果你在使用Hexo时遇到任何问题，你可以在[故障排除]（https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html）中找到答案，或者你可以在[GitHub]（https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues）上问我。</a></p><h2 id="快速启动"><a href="#快速启动" class="headerlink" title="快速启动"></a>快速启动</h2><h3 id="创建一个新帖子"><a href="#创建一个新帖子" class="headerlink" title="创建一个新帖子"></a>创建一个新帖子</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息：[写作]（<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html%EF%BC%89">https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html）</a></p><h3 id="运行服务"><a href="#运行服务" class="headerlink" title="运行服务"></a>运行服务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息：[服务器]（<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html%EF%BC%89">https://hexo.io/docs/server.html）</a></p><h3 id="生成静态文件"><a href="#生成静态文件" class="headerlink" title="生成静态文件"></a>生成静态文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息：[生成]（<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html%EF%BC%89">https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html）</a></p><h3 id="部署到远程站点"><a href="#部署到远程站点" class="headerlink" title="部署到远程站点"></a>部署到远程站点</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息：[部署]（<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html%EF%BC%89">https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html）</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
    
    
